3. Using ScalaTion



4. Building and Installing

To build the ScalaTion system, simply compile and run the included Build.scala
script.

> cd scalation 
> scalac Build.scala 
> scala Build


5. Mailing Lists / Contact



6. Source Code

The latest version of the source code is available in the subversion repository.
Use this command to anonymously check out the latest project source code:

> svn checkout http://scalation.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ scalation

